reviewText: The box and tape have a 1989 copyright date.  There is a copyright notice for Roger Rabbit 1991 at the end of the tape.  The first 15 minutes are devoted to Disney World and 20th anniversary coverage.  The last 5 minutes shows you what the GM World Of Motion pavilion and ride was like before Test Track was built.

This is a 1993 promotional video for Walt Disney World Resorts & theme parks with a focus on Epcot Center/World Showcase & the Magic Kingdom. Sponsored by General Motors, this is still enjoyable to watch today.
